title: Hellllllllllllll yeah! I'm full build now and I got Q farm galore - Nasus
body:
{{champion:75}}: heck yes! Gonna rip this adc a new one!

{{champion:67}}: hur, shert erp nersus, lert ers hurnt thers thert farr ernto derkners 

{{champion:56}}: THATS RACIST VAYNE.

{{champion:75}}: shut up VAYNE! Here I come! Argh fury of the sands! Ghost, I choose you!

{{champion:412}} : I can't let you do that, Nasus.

{{champion:75}} : lol what the heck? What are you going to to, Thresh? You have like no gold and 3 items. I'm a full build Nasus with my Q all farmed up. Out of my way ghostass.

{{champion:412}} *flay*

{{champion:75}} : wtf!!!! You knocked me back and Vayne chunked me...shit, gotta run I guess.

{{champion:412}} *death sentence*

{{champion:75}} : wtf??? Let me go!

{{champion:67}} : hurggggg purred w/ sawdust. *right clicks*

{{champion:75}} : fuck. This is bullshit, now I'm dead. Thresh had nothing and he made a mighty Nasus useless. Fuck this. Tower time.

{{champion:412}} : I can't let you do that, Nasus.

{{champion:75}} : oh yeah? Try and stop me. *qs tower*

{{champion:412}} :*flay* *lanterns in vayne*

{{champion:75}} : GOD DAMNIT NAPPA

{{champion:67}} : parched w/ simba! *right clicks*


20 minutes after the game.

{{champion:75}} : God damnit that game sucked, I did everything right. I got farmed, I hit like a truck, I was a god! That stupid zero cs, 3 item Tresh is bullshit! Oh well, at least I have this delicious sandwich! Yum!

{{champion:412}} : I can't let you do that, Nasus. *flays sandwich*

{{champion:75}} : ARRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRGH
